# gen167 (E1 reflexive, capstone): parrot0 RUNS its own composition. Asked to
# prove its parts compose by running it itself, it spins up a fresh copy of
# itself (brain_create), feeds the dialogue derived from its module(X) self-model
# through brain_respond, checks each part actually fired, and reports the verdict
# computed from real output — not a canned string. Footprint-free on the live
# brain; it still touches no files and commits nothing (anti-self-management).
> prove your parts compose by running it yourself
< I ran it on a fresh copy of myself: knowledge, abduce and robust — 3 of 3 parts fired and cooperated in one dialogue. Composition holds (PASS). No file was touched; an external agent still owns edits and commits.